            "title": "即月期指開跌193點   低水210點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報25507，跌193點或0.75%，低水210點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科指期貨開報4990，跌36點或0.72%，低水38點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國指期貨開報8650，跌40點或0.46%，低水50點。</p>\n</div>",
