        {
            "title": "東方海外去年盈利跌41%  末期息減逾68%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">東方海外(00316)公布，去年盈利按年跌41.24%至15.15億美元，派末期息每股0.42美元或3.276港元，按年減68.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內，收入跌9.15%至97.2億美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240104_FI_source-web_00316.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240104_FI_source-web_00316.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：東方海外官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司表示，中東局勢的變化為未來市場走勢增添了變數。地緣政治事件似乎越發頻繁出現，任何一個地緣政治因素都有可能瞬間起效而且可能帶來漣漪效應，很難準確預判市場走勢，唯有做好自己的事，謹慎行事、順勢而為、主動應對。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，去年集團一共接收9艘16828個標準箱型全新集裝箱船舶，至此16828個標準箱系列船舶已經全部交付使用並投入運營。這不僅加強其在太平洋航線的服務能力，亞歐航線上原本因運力不足而暫停運營的LL3航線也間接得以恢復。今年續有新船陸續交付，包括24000個標準箱型甲醇雙燃料集裝箱船和從Seaspan Corporation的子公司租入的13580個標準箱型傳統燃料集裝箱船。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15735729-%e6%9d%b1%e6%96%b9%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c41-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%b8%9b%e9%80%be68",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250313_FI_source-web_00316-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 09:21:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "太古折讓9.6%配售國泰航空   籌17.89億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">太古(00019)今早公布配售國泰航空(00293)股份，作價11.74元，較昨日收市價12.99 元折讓約 9.6%；出售股份相當已發行國泰航空股份總數約 2.52%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：國泰官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250806_FI_source-web_00293-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國泰官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250806_FI_source-web_00293-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：國泰官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，同意出售，而配售代理同意以個別責任形式尋找承配人購買，或在未能尋找到承配人時由其本身購買，共計 1.53億股出售股份。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">預期所得款項淨額約17.89億元，擬將配售事項所得款項淨額用作一般營運資金用途。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集團預期就配售事項錄得約3.65億元之收益。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">是次配售事項將使太古於國泰航空的持股，回復至國泰航空向 Qatar Airways Group Q.C.S.C.進行場外股份回購完成前的歷史水平，於公告日期，太古在國泰航空中擁有約 47.64%權益。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事局認為，透過配售事項籌集資金對公司具有裨益，將可增加其營運資金、進一步強化其資產負債表及提高其財務靈活性。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736487-%e5%a4%aa%e5%8f%a4%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%939-6%e9%85%8d%e5%94%ae%e5%9c%8b%e6%b3%b0%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba-%e7%b1%8c17-89%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-101424_source-web_00019-1_source-web_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 09:16:05",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期跌225點  ADR低水142點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期報25484 點，跌225 點或0.88%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨日收市低水142點或0.56%，報25573點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_HSBC-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_HSBC-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍金融股跌，滙控(00005)倫敦股價跌3.5%，ADR則較港股收市低0.2%，折合港元計收報128.62元; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣83.26元，較香港收市價低1.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低0.2%，報131.3元。騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣541.41元，較香港收市價低0.9% ; 美團 (03690)ADR收市折合港幣75.61元，較香港收市價低1.4% ;小米(01810) ADR收市折合港幣33.34元，較香港收市價0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報25467點，跌233點，較昨日恒指收市25716點，低水250點，成交23996張。國指夜市期指收報8635點，較昨日國指收市低水65點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736468-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c225%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4142%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 09:01:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價升逾9%　創逾3年半收市新高　布蘭特期油升穿100美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原油期貨價格急升逾9%，創逾3年半收市新高，布蘭特期油升穿每桶100元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">伊朗新任最高領袖穆傑塔巴表示，霍爾木茲海峽應該保持關閉，加上持續有運油輪被襲擊。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油收報每桶95.73美元，上升8.48美元，升幅9.72%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5月倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶100.46美元，上升8.48美元，升幅9.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">有分析指，市場嚴重失衡的局面將持續至霍爾木茲海峽重開、上下游作業恢復正常，但需要時間。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736257-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be9%e3%80%80%e5%89%b5%e9%80%be3%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8a%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e5%b8%83%e8%98%ad%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%9f%e6%b2%b9%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf100-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/8a6d6fb35c89d9b0db4c4846f290c2c3_Iran_US_Oil_Prices_19824_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 08:56:08",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "道指挫739點納指跌1.78%   金融股瀉　兩年期國債息率飆12.6基點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股跌逾1.5%至近2%。道瓊斯工業平均指數及標普500指數連跌3日，「恐慌指數」的VIX波動指數一度抽高12.3%，至27.22。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/9015cbc7db4569fddd124659acfcaf86_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_41161_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/9015cbc7db4569fddd124659acfcaf86_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_41161_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中東局勢持續緊張，伊朗新任最高領袖穆傑塔巴表示，霍爾木茲海峽應該保持關閉，加上有運油輪被襲擊，油價急升逾9%，加劇市場對通脹的擔憂，令大市受壓。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯工業平均指數跌穿47000點，收報46677點，跌739點或1.56%。早段低開174點後，跌幅最多擴大至755點，最低見46662點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納斯達克指數收報22311點，跌404點，跌幅1.78%，一度下滑1.87%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">標準普爾500指數失守6700點，收報6672點，跌103點，跌幅1.52%，曾挫1.56%，11個主要板塊中，能源板塊升幅最大，上升1%。工業板塊跌2.5%，跌幅最大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">摩根士丹利及Cliffwater限制旗下私募基金贖回，觸發大型銀行及另類資產管理公司股價新一輪拋售，大摩插水4.1%，摩根大通下調部分向私募信貸基金提供貸款的估值，股價跌近2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">高盛滑落4.4%，為跌幅最大道指成份股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">花旗挫超過3%，Blue Owl及KKR跌幅分別為4.5%及3.7%。此外，德銀披露其在私募信貸市場的曝險金額達260億歐元，股價應聲下滑逾5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nvidia、蘋果公司及特斯拉(Tesla)股價分別跌1.5%、1.9%和3.1%。Meta及Tesla跌近3%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國10年期債息最多倒升7個基點，報4.277厘，對息口較敏感的2年期債息急飆12.6個基點，至3.762厘。美滙指數一度上揚0.52%，報99.75，</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736259-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab739%e9%bb%9e%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c1-78-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%80%89%e3%80%80%e5%85%a9%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e5%9c%8b%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e9%a3%8612-6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240805_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 08:47:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股低收   滙控倫敦股價跌3.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲3大指數連跌兩日。中東衝突導致油價急升，投資者擔憂令通脹上升，不利經濟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.61%，報598點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230718-164936_00005-20180504_FI_Britain-HSBC_0005_FB-1-1-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230718-164936_00005-20180504_FI_Britain-HSBC_0005_FB-1-1-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國富時100指數收報10305點，跌48點，跌幅0.47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">法國CAC指數失守8000點，收報7984點，跌57點，跌幅0.71%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數收報23589點，跌50點，跌幅0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報44456點，低走0.71%或316點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報17139點，下挫1.22%或212點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)倫敦股價下跌3.5%，報11.958英鎊，折合約124.9港元，較本港收市128.9元低3.1%。集團決定無限期關閉旗下卡塔爾分支機構，此前，伊朗宣布將打擊區內與美國和以色列相關的經濟和銀行資產。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國汽車巨頭寶馬(BMW)股價攀升1.1%。集團表示，2025年純利錄得超過70億歐元，略高於市場預期。然而汽車產業面臨的關稅負擔，將使寶馬汽車部門今年的息稅前利潤率下降約1.25個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736261-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%80%ab%e6%95%a6%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e8%b7%8c3-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 08:36:07",
